.special-form      
  form.special-form__form(@submit.prevent='validate', method='post', v-if='!formSubmitted')
    
    .special-form__group
      input.special-form__input(name='fullName', v-model='fullName', v-validate="'required|alpha_spaces'", :class="{ 'special-form__input--error': errors.has('fullName') }", type='text')
      label.special-form__label(:class="{ 'special-form__label--active': fullName }") Nombre
      .special-form__message(v-show="errors.has('fullName')") Se requiere el nombre.
    
    .special-form__group.special-form__group--half
      input.special-form__input(name='clientEmail', v-model='clientEmail', v-validate="'required|email'", :class="{ 'input': true, 'special-form__input--error': errors.has('clientEmail') }")
      label.special-form__label(:class="{ 'special-form__label--active': clientEmail }") E-mail
      .special-form__message(v-show="errors.has('clientEmail')")  Por favor ponga un E-mail válido
    
    .special-form__group.special-form__group--half
      input.special-form__input(name='clientPhone', v-model='clientPhone', v-validate="'required|numeric'", :class="{ 'input': true, 'special-form__input--error': errors.has('clientPhone') }")
      label.special-form__label(:class="{ 'special-form__label--active': clientPhone }") Teléfono
      .special-form__message(v-show="errors.has('clientPhone')") Por favor ponga un número de teléfono válido, solo números
    
    .special-form__group.special-form__group-message
      textarea.special-form__input(name='comments', v-model='comments', v-validate="'required'", :class="{ 'input': true, 'special-form__input--error': errors.has('comments') }")
      label.special-form__label(:class="{ 'special-form__label--active': comments }") Comentarios
      .special-form__message(v-show="errors.has('comments')") Por favor ponga una razón para contactarnos
    
    .special-form__button-group
      .special-form__submit-button.active(@click='validate')
        span Enviar
  transition(name='fade-in')
    h1.special-form__thank-you(v-if='formSuccess && formSubmitted') Gracias Por Contactarnos!
  transition(name='fade-in')
    .special-form__sending-overlay(v-if='!formSuccess && formSubmitted')
      h1.special-form__sending Enviando
        span .
        span .
        span .
